    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A dull yellow compact marble with irregular veins and blotches of dull terracotta red; it also sometimes contains patches of white crystalline calcite. Found in Catalonia in northern Spain and in Siena, Italy.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
